.com/news/tv/squid-game-the-challenge-is-the-most-viewed-show-on-netflix-this-week-3550626">成为本周平台上观看最多的节目</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-fans-are-raving-about-this-new-binge-worthy-swedish-crime-thriller-3550877">Netflix的帖子粉丝对这款新的狂欢瑞典犯罪惊悚片引起了人们的欢迎，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
